request.description:
Admin login endpoint. Returns admin details if credentials are correct.

**Sample Request:**
```json
{
    "email": "admin@mlmusik.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}
```

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Login successful",
    "admin": {
        "id": 1,
        "email": "admin@mlmusik.com",
        "createdAt": "2024-01-01T10:00:00"
    }
}
```

