request.description:
Increment the view count for a song. Call this endpoint when a user plays a song.

**Sample Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "song": {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Shape of You",
        "views": 1,
        ...
    }
}
```

Increment the share count and get a shareable URL.

**Sample Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "shareableUrl": "http://localhost:8080/api/songs/1",
    "song": {
        "id": 1,
        "shares": 1,
        ...
    }
}
```
